BP Plc,  Europe ’s second-biggest oil
company, agreed to pay Reliance Industries Ltd. $7.2 billion for
stakes in 23 blocks in  India , expanding operations in  Asia ’s
third-biggest economy.  To contact the reporters on this story:  Andrew MacAskill in  New Delhi  at 
